{{refimprove|date=January 2018}} {{For|the film of a similar name|Utopians (film)}} {{Italic title}} '''''Ütopya''''' is the Turkish version of the Dutch TV series ''[[Utopia (Dutch reality TV series)|Utopia]]'', created by [[John de Mol]]. The series follows a group of people who attempt to maintain a society in a remote area. The format was bought by [[Acun Ilıcalı]] and his television Tv8 began airing ''Ütopya'' on October 30, 2014.<ref>http://www.milliyet.com.tr/utopya-bu-aksam-basliyor--magazin-1961816/</ref> Tuncay Kes finished the show as the champion.
